Subject: [PATCH] Align examples repo with current template systematic

Update the custom Timeline and Catalog templates to use the same
records_list_types systematic for shared heading rendering and TYPO3
core sanitize.html handling of backend fragments. Refresh README and
TSconfig wording so custom view type terminology matches the main
extension documentation.
