 README.md                                     | 18 ++++++----
 .../Backend/Templates/CatalogView.html        | 34 ++++++-------------
 .../Backend/Templates/TimelineView.html       | 30 +++++-----------
 4 files changed, 37 insertions(+), 53 deletions(-)

